nt||at|mitche: DONT ("Disturb Opponents NoTrump) works like this
If you have a 2-suited hand, 5-5 (or a good 5-4), you bid the lower - ranking suit.
In DONT - N bids 2@C, saying "clubs plus a higher ranking suit".. If N bids 2@d, it says @D's and 1 major
2@h means "both majors"
and 2@s means "long spades, not much else"
If you have a GOOD one-suiter, then you double 1NT|
